{"tid":2318842,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[絲入] 垃圾謝沇錤豐胸","createTime":"2020-12-09T15:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T00:15:30.000Z","uid":232103,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d93570c20fbf29abf2742985f3b2a7da247ba7cb","tid":2318842,"uid":232103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:41:14.000Z","msg":"借post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔好再信推幾推可以豐到胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係咁 香港周街都係大波妹<br />\n<br />\n講返 <span class=\"xx-large\">謝沇錤</span><br />\n身邊好多絲打都以為咁出名咁貴應該有啲用<br />\n宜家加到三四千蚊一次療程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五千蚊一樽仔豐胸膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要迫人一炮過買幾萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加加埋埋可以用成十幾萬至幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有效都唔緊要<br />\n最重要係 一！啲！效！果！都！冇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到都有好幾個post講緊做過 但完全冇效<br />\n點解仲有咁多蠢豬豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推哂成副身家落去買一樣一啲效都冇嘅嘢<br />\n支持一間咁撚戇鳩嘅公司<br />\n連出街見到佢啲濕鳩廣告都.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奉勸各位絲打/妹妹仔唔好再倒錢落海<br />\n等謝小姐快撚啲執柒咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8afdb2a1780b956bba4da5d2c34cf174ccb8ec","tid":2318842,"uid":17387,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"係咪你本身IPAD所以無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8728cc59b804700e6c2350ec2a588576df1dab","tid":2318842,"uid":131836,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"豐胸係要本身有胸先有得豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw收據同胸圖都無張好難信你"},{"pid":"09723c365bb359b3e92a32b8d2ae7383459d7ebb","tid":231884